---

---

<section class="relative mb-20 md:mb-32 overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Decorative background texture -->
  <div
    class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none select-none"
    aria-hidden="true"
  >
    <div
      class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-64 h-64 opacity-[0.04] rounded-full bg-[#5E0B15] blur-3xl -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2"
    >
    </div>
    <div
      class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-96 h-96 opacity-[0.04] rounded-full bg-[#5E0B15] blur-3xl translate-x-1/3 translate-y-1/3"
    >
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Badge + Heading row -->
  <div
    class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 md:gap-6 items-end relative"
  >
    <!-- Left: Headline -->
    <div class="lg:col-span-8 about-hero-heading" data-scroll-reveal data-reveal-delay="0">
      <span
        class="bg-[#2e0007] text-[#ffdadb] text-[10px] px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full font-label uppercase tracking-widest mb-6 inline-block letter-spacing-widest"
      >
        Desde 2023
      </span>
      <h1
        class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-[5rem] leading-[0.9] text-[#5E0B15] tracking-tighter font-headline"
      >
        <span class="block italic font-semibold pb-2 md:pb-4"
          >Hacia un nuevo enfoque</span
        >
        <span class="block font-black not-italic relative">
          del Derecho del Trabajo
          <!-- Underline accent -->
          <span
            class="absolute -bottom-3 left-0 w-24 h-[3px] bg-[#5E0B15] rounded-full hero-underline"
          ></span>
        </span>
      </h1>
    </div>

    <!-- Right: Description -->
    <div class="lg:col-span-4 pb-2 about-hero-desc" data-scroll-reveal data-reveal-delay="150">
      <!-- Vertical divider (desktop) -->
      <div class="hidden lg:block w-px h-16 bg-[#5E0B15]/20 mb-6 ml-2"></div>
      <p class="font-body text-base md:text-lg text-[#564243] leading-relaxed">
        En DETRA-UNT nos encontramos en la intersección de la tradición legal y
        la exploración académica moderna. Nuestro compromiso con la excelencia
        editorial define cada publicación y evento.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Bottom decorative rule -->
  <div class="mt-16 md:mt-20 flex items-center gap-4 about-hero-rule" data-scroll-reveal data-reveal-delay="300">
    <div
      class="h-px flex-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#5E0B15]/30 via-[#5E0B15]/10 to-transparent"
    >
    </div>
    <span
      class="font-label text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-[#5E0B15]/50"
      >DETRA · UNT · Derecho Laboral</span
    >
    <div class="h-px w-12 bg-[#5E0B15]/20"></div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  /* Staggered reveal animations */
  @keyframes fadeSlideUp {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(24px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }

  @keyframes expandWidth {
    from {
      transform: scaleX(0);
    }
    to {
      transform: scaleX(1);
    }
  }

  .about-hero-heading {
    animation: fadeSlideUp 0.7s ease;
  }

  .about-hero-desc {
    animation: fadeSlideUp 0.7s ease;
    animation-delay: 0.15s;
  }

  .about-hero-rule {
    animation: fadeSlideUp 0.7s ease;
    animation-delay: 0.1s;
  }

  .hero-underline {
    transform-origin: left center;
    animation: expandWidth 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
    animation-delay: 0.35s;
  }
</style>
